Third Department,

August, 1958

(August 8, 1958) In the Matter of Lloyd R. Le Fever, Petitioner, against Louis J. Lefkowitz, as Attorney-General of the State of New York, Respondent.

Appeal dismissed, on the ground that the order appealed from is not appealable. (Matter of Ryan [Hogan], 306 N. Y. 11; Matter of Turecamo Gontr. Co., 260 App. Div. 253.) Foster, P. J., Bergan, Coon and Gibson, JJ., concur.
